## Description
The&nbsp;**Archive Documents (DA-hotspot)** task allows to load and archive documents into the Digital Archiving 3 software service using the legacy Digital Archiving Endpoint configuration.

> Important

This is a legacy task created to support the migration to Digital Archiving 3 build 3.37 (January 2023 release). For all new applications, please refer to the latest version of the task:&nbsp;[Archive Documents (DA) On-Demand Workflow Task Reference](/doxee-platform/docs/archive-documents-da-hotspot-on-demand-workflow-task-reference).

## Configuration
![](data:image/png;base64,)

- In the&nbsp;**Alias** field, enter the name of the task that will be displayed in the workflow.

- Click on the&nbsp;**Store &gt;&nbsp;Resource** field and select the Digital Archiving Hotspot resource to use.

> Note

For more information, see:&nbsp;[Digital Archiving Hotspot Resource Reference](/doxee-platform/docs/digital-archiving-hotspot-resource-reference).

- In the&nbsp;**Input &gt; Index pattern**, enter the&nbsp;name of the XML index file or a filename pattern (in glob format) to identify it.

> Note

The default value is&nbsp;*LOADER.DA.INDEX.xml*.

> Note

For more information on the structure of the DA3 Loader index file, see:&nbsp;[Digital Archiving 3 Loader Index File](/doxee-platform/docs/digital-archiving-3-loader-index-file).
